<C>__{anonymous older man}
<D>__{remember brinkley's great line "it's as irrevocable as a haircut."}
<A>__{now, on the second level, she scans the crowd. jane's p.o.v. the floor below. tom in the world's best fitting tux... clusters of people from around him but he works his way easily through them as he looks for jane and grins his greetings, men are buoyed, women's pulses throb.}
<B>__{on jane}
<A>__{as she silently mouths the words "smile and move and smile and move." which is exactly what he's doing. then a contract with the gods.}
